EN: I have been designated as the team captain.

ZH: 请在指定位置等候。
EN: Please wait at the designated location.

ZH: 他被指定为公司的新总裁。
EN: He was designated as the new CEO of the company.

ZH: 这个区域指定为非吸烟区。
EN: This area is designated as a non-smoking zone.

ZH: 你可以指定一个代理人代表你处理这个问题。
EN: You can designate an agent to handle this matter on your behalf.

ZH: 请指定你的收货地址。
EN: Please specify your shipping address.

