EN: This matter needs to be assigned to a specific person.

ZH: 我无法指定你的具体职责。
EN: I cannot specify your exact responsibilities.

ZH: 这个房间被指定给了你。
EN: This room has been assigned to you.

ZH: 请指定你对此事的立场。
EN: Please indicate your stance on this matter.

